prices fell by 22 % during the reference period .
( 86 ) The prices charged by the Community industry and the exporting manufacturers in the country concerned in the UZ on the Community market were compared .
prices were compared after deduction of all discounts and quantity discounts .
the prices of the Community industry were taken to the factory level , and import prices were based on the cif @ prices free frontier of the Community .
( 87 ) The comparison showed that imports of the goods concerned were sold in the Community UZ at prices below the prices of the Community sector ( expressed as a percentage of the prices of the Community sector ) .
In view of this undercut price range and the development of Community economic prices described above , it is clear that prices have already been significantly reduced .
5 . Situation of the Community industry
88 . Pursuant to Article 3 ( 5 ) of the Basic Regulation , the examination of the impact of dumped imports on the Community industry included an assessment of all economic factors and indices affecting the situation of the Community sector from 2001 ( base year ) to the UZ .
( 89 ) The following information on the Community industry is the aggregated data of the four cooperating Community manufacturers .
5.1 Production , production capacity and capacity utilization
( 90 ) Production , production capacity and capacity utilization developed as follows :
