( 91 ) As the above table shows , production declined by 9 % in the reference period .
to save costs , production capacity was reduced by 16 % , resulting in an 8 % increase in capacity utilization .
5.2 Inventories
( 92 ) The following table shows the inventories for the annual financial statements .
