amending Regulation ( EC ) No 1159 / 2003 laying down implementing provisions for the import of cane sugar under certain tariff quotas and preferential agreements for the marketing years 2003 / 04 , 2004 / 05 and 2005 / 06 and amending Regulations ( EC ) No 1464 / 95 and ( EC ) No 779 / 96
COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES
