Having regard to Council Regulation ( EC ) No 1260 / 2001 of 19 June 2001 on the common organisation of the market in sugar &#91; 1 &#93; , in particular Articles 22 ( 2 ) and 39 ( 6 ) thereof ,
Having regard to Council Regulation ( EC ) No 1095 / 96 of 18 June 1996 on the application of concessions in accordance with the list CXL drawn up after the conclusion of the negotiations under Article XXIV ( 6 ) of the GATT &#91; 2 &#93; , in particular Article 1 thereof ,
Considering the following reasons :
