2 . In order to ensure the predictability necessary for the proper settlement of trade transactions , the Commission should provisionally determine the quantities of delivery obligations in accordance with the procedure laid down in Article 42 ( 2 ) of Regulation ( EC ) No 1260 / 2001 before the start of the relevant delivery period .
( 3 ) During the delivery period , these quantities shall be determined - as soon as the actual deliveries from previous years are better known - with the possibility of a change should even more precise information be available at a later date .
