( 2 ) The amount of pipe ice currently stored by the Greek intervention site is very extensive and the storage time is very long .
For this reason , a permanent tender for resale on the internal market of around 18,000 tonnes of pipe ice from stocks of this intervention site should be opened .
( 3 ) The measures provided for in this Regulation are in line with the opinion of the Management Committee for Cereals -
has FOLLOWING REGULATION :
Article 1
