Article 2
( 1 ) The offer period for the first partial tender expires on 27 April 2005 .
( 2 ) The offer period for the last partial tender expires on 29 June 2005 .
( 3 ) The offers shall be deposited with the Greek Intervention Centre :
OPEKEPE
Acharnon Street 241
GR -@ 10446 Athens
Telephone : ( 30 – 210 ) 212 48 46 and 212 47 88
Fax : ( 30 – 210 ) 212 47 91 .
Article 3
